Quickstrike:





Quickstrike looked up and stood up. He calmed down a little. He looked at 
Dark Mouse.

"Who is coming?" a voice asked. Quickstrike jolted, and nearly lost his 
balanace. It was Megatron's voice. He hated it when he came out of no where 
wanting to know what was going on. Quickstrike had some things to hide a 
while ago.

Megatron came to Dark Mouse's side and looked at them both in beast mode. He 
lowered his head to their level. Quickstrike lowered his head, a little 
unsteady on his legs.
